Classes/OTOModule.html.name: OTOModule
Classes/OTOModule.html.abstract: OTOModule represents an instance of a module. Modules contain functionality associated with a product. For example a video module will present video content about a particular product on the 121nexus platform.

Classes/OTOImageUploadModule.html.name: OTOImageUploadModule
Classes/OTOImageUploadModule.html.abstract: OTOImageUploadModule is a module that allows a user to upload photos to the 121nexus platform.

Classes/OTOGudidModule.html.name: OTOGudidModule
Classes/OTOGudidModule.html.abstract: OTOGudidModule is a module that allows users to look up medical devices via barcode data in the FDA’s GUDID access database. It provides information about a medical device submitted to the FDA by the manufacturer.

Classes/OTOVideoModule.html.name: OTOVideoModule
Classes/OTOVideoModule.html.abstract: OTOVideoModule is a video module that allows a user to view video content stored on the 121nexus platform. This can be direct video files or videos hosted on video hosting services like YouTube.

Classes/OTOGs1ValidationModule.html.name: OTOGs1ValidationModule
Classes/OTOGs1ValidationModule.html.abstract: OTOGs1ValidationModule is a module that validates barcode data based on GS1’s barcode parsing rules. GS1 General Spec

Classes/OTOTextModule.html.name: OTOTextModule
Classes/OTOTextModule.html.abstract: OTOTextModule is a text module that allows a user to display text content stored on teh 121nexus platform.

Classes/OTOSurveyModule.html.name: OTOSurveyModule
Classes/OTOSurveyModule.html.abstract: OTOSurveyModule is a module that allows users to present survey type content. There are 3 types of survey questions: Select, Text, and Date.

Classes/OTOCustomValidationModule.html.name: OTOCustomValidationModule
Classes/OTOCustomValidationModule.html.abstract: OTOCustomValidationModule is a module that allows a user to run custom validations on barcodes with rules created on the 121nexus Platform.

Classes/OTOExperience.html.name: OTOExperience
Classes/OTOExperience.html.abstract: The OTOExperience class defines an experience of a scanned product. Experiences are comprised of one or more modules that a user can interact with. Experiences let users watch video, upload photos, validate data and display content.

Classes/OTOSession.html.name: OTOSession
Classes/OTOSession.html.abstract: OTOSession is a class that allows you to start a session to track user interactions with an experience.

Classes/OTOProduct.html.name: OTOProduct
Classes/OTOProduct.html.abstract: OTOProduct is a class that represents a physical product on the 121nexus platform. Products can be searched by the barcode data or by unique urls found on the system.

Classes/OTOCaptureView.html#/s:8OTOnexus.name: delegate
Classes/OTOCaptureView.html#/s:8OTOnexus.abstract: Main delegate that has two methods associated with it didCapture(product:OTOProduct) and scannedBarcodeDoesNotExist(barcode:String)

Classes/OTOCaptureView.html#/s:8OTOnexus.name: isBarcodeTypeHidden
Classes/OTOCaptureView.html#/s:8OTOnexus.abstract: Bool value to turn hide/show barcode type segmented control

Classes/OTOCaptureView.html.name: OTOCaptureView
Classes/OTOCaptureView.html.abstract: OTOCaptureView is a class that provides scanning functionality to capture barcodes and provide the data associated with them. Through its delegate methods it returns the raw barcode string that can be used to search on the 121nexus platform
